quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  106,1,The union of the people of Qoraish into one whole body
  106,2,And the safety of their customary trade journeys winter and summer
  106,3,"Are owed to Allah, the Sovereign of this Sanctuary -AL-Ka’ba- Whom they should worship, and Him alone they should adore"
  106,4,He saved them from hunger and gave them the security they longed for